findings.title: Owner privileges (In the period when the owner is not renounced)
findings.description: The contract owner has excessive privileges to change various parameters and settings, including maximum transaction amount, dividends, fees, wallet percentage, swap threshold, target liquidity values, distribution criteria, and more.

findings.title: Out of gas exception if there will be a long receivers list
findings.description: The function makeItRain() uses a loop to airdrop rewards by the list and will be aborted with OUT_OF_GAS exception if there will be a long receivers list.
